      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide for the establishment of a commission to engage in an informed, national, and public dialogue about how to ensure that each student in the United States receives an equitable education that enables the student to achieve his or her maximum academic potential.</title>
      </item>
